{"tid":1526990,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我支持警察執法","createTime":"2019-09-01T08:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T09:51:18.000Z","uid":62032,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"da3f9c8565863069e6f50a95c5fb6959830f956b","tid":1526990,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:26:00.000Z","msg":"我<span style=\"color: red;\">支持警察執法</span>,<br />\n但我<span style=\"color: red;\">唔支持警察</span>。<br />\n<br />\n更多更多嘅人行出嚟反抗,<br />\n唔係因為反警察本身,<br />\n而係係反對<span style=\"color: blue;\">警察唔守法</span>。<br />\n<br />\n示威者做緊嘅係<span style=\"color: blue;\">公民抗命,<br />\n有時多多少少會涉及違法行為</span>。<br />\n但呢種違法,<br />\n係基於「社會良知及正義」之類公共利益的重視,<br />\n無辦法之下用嚟喚起多數人認同的非常手段。<br />\n冇人想坐監,但有一班勇敢嘅人企出嚟話佢哋唔怕,<br />\n佢哋願意付出十年嘅青春去救返我哋嘅香港。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">當大家都有心理準備去公民抗命畀人拉,<br />\n有冇諗過點解會由反惡法變咗反黑警呢?</span><br />\n<br />\n喺一個<del><span style=\"color: blue;\">法治(rule of law)社會</span></del>,<br />\n法律係管治者嘅工具,<br />\n不單止用嚟規範市民行為,<br />\n更重要嘅係佢它限制埋政府嘅公權力,<br />\n令政府都受法律所規管。<br />\n<br />\n由強推送中修訂,<br />\n到恐嚇要戒嚴,出緊急法,<br />\n香港社會就已經步入<del><span style=\"color: blue;\">以法管治(rule by law)</span></del>嘅階段 - 政府制定同以法律作為管治手段/工具,<br />\n去達到佢哋想要嘅效果。<br />\n呢個時候，法律就已經失去咗限制政府嘅公權力,<br />\n簡稱冇王法。<br />\n<br />\n由69開始，香港警察選擇性執法,<br />\n因為你政治立場唔同/幫緊嘅人唔同,<br />\n一啲人就頭破血流被控暴動,<br />\n另一啲人就拍拍膊頭就可以走,<br />\n拎武器打人都話睇唔倒。<br />\n嗰時開始,<br />\n就已經變成<strong><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">人治社會(rule by man)</span></em></strong> - <span style=\"color: blue;\">政府講嘅嘢就係王法,<br />\n想點定性就定性，想點處理案件就點處理,<br />\n冇統一標準可言,</span><br />\n簡稱<span style=\"color: blue;\">法治已死</span>。<br />\n<br />\n有人犯法, <br />\n警察可以拉佢 + 問足佢48 + 送佢上court受法律制裁。<br />\n但放過斬人疑犯/控以較輕罪名;<br />\n做嘢唔出示委任證;<br />\n用武器唔跟守則;<br />\n見倒疑似異見人士就毆打控以重罪, 連記者採訪都禁止, 要經安排先拍攝...<br />\n咁樣選擇性執法...執法?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">警察根本唔係執緊法,<br />\n只係幫政府以執法為由打壓異見人士同反對聲音。</span><br />\n<br />\n我之前睇過辛灝年嘅一段片<br />\n我愛中國，你愛中共。<br />\n同一樣道理，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我支持警察執法, 你支持警察。</span></span>"},{"pid":"5d86cce19729bd0e5e6b964d008675751c8c69ab","tid":1526990,"uid":230890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:27:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7271b987833740e9c16c3f5b8f39241e23864871","tid":1526990,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"用唔犯法既行為對抗政權先係出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc593da8be8a8abb5766f700bbbc49e9d6d13fc","tid":1526990,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:27:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"245b37d5f6976bc3dc1c827a00cbff0a8576c90a","tid":1526990,"uid":62032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d86cce19729bd0e5e6b964d008675751c8c69ab","tid":1526990,"uid":230890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:27:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:29:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警唔係執法者<br />\n係黑社會<br />\n死全家係啱<br />\n黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5a15879b1d7131b45324c3e0cef83fd61e43c901","tid":1526990,"uid":303349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:37:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公民抗命其實一早預咗畀人拉，只不過而家濫捕、唔人道拉人同選擇性「執法」絕對不為人所接受<br />\n問題唔在於警察執法，而在於警察如何執法"},{"pid":"749b592e0d5d71e33b22f865915f742ef1e2a4e7","tid":1526990,"uid":303349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a15879b1d7131b45324c3e0cef83fd61e43c901","tid":1526990,"uid":303349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:37:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公民抗命其實一早預咗畀人拉，只不過而家濫捕、唔人道拉人同選擇性「執法」絕對不為人所接受<br />\n問題唔在於警察執法，而在於警察如何執法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:38:49.000Z","msg":"利申：黑警冚家剷"},{"pid":"c04e792e14982fd2fc2efcf384c590abf31c6b0f","tid":1526990,"uid":288777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:39:04.000Z","msg":"講得好啱 有point"},{"pid":"2f336a81f36cd83ca1b0cf6793ae33a689b951ca","tid":1526990,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:39:42.000Z","msg":"我係想帶出話支持警察執法嗰班友嘅問題:<br />\n佢哋只係支持警察<br />\n而唔係支持緊警察執法/法治<br />\n<br />\n而家班友成日覺得自己啱<br />\n係因為佢哋放咗自己上道德高地<br />\n當自己係正義，就拎鐵通打人都當啱<br />\n831入黨鐵721 2.0都啱<br />\n<br />\n我哋明知佢哋自我催眠<br />\n點解唔去拮爆佢個春秋大夢？<br />\n<br />\n你哋起我底就知我係乜人<br />\n如果有警察係正常執法我會支持<br />\n但過咗721<br />\n我係覺得所有警察都係黑警<br />\n諗清楚我講乜<br />\n更唔係要洗白<br />\n你哋鐘意負就負啦"},{"pid":"178b1bdb8da88c3b073f2c0f9d387ac5fcc2b2aa","tid":1526990,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60488f18e3cf96996d51cce1e885679232704094","tid":1526990,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b44aba8560cf4192145ceeccd6b7dafbacace1","tid":1526990,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"btw機場呀！<br />\n人呢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr